    <div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Xbox Game Studios [965 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/xbox-game-studios">Xbox Game Studios</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Halo Studios [135 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/xbox-game-studios/halo-studios">Halo Studios</a> have released the official story trailer for <em>Halo: Combat Evolved</em> remake <em><a title="Games > Halo: Campaign Evolved [2 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/halo-campaign-evolved">Halo: Campaign Evolved</a></em>. The trailer was captured on a <a title="Platforms > PS5 [11,514 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a> Pro. <span id="more-1056999"></span></p><p><em>Halo: Campaign Evolved</em> is due out for PlayStation 5, <a title="Platforms > Xbox Series [8,796 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/xbox/xbox-series">Xbox Series</a>, and <a title="Platforms > PC [25,613 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/pc">PC</a> via <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/2806050/Halo_Campaign_Evolved/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Steam</a> and <a href="https://www.xbox.com/en-US/games/store/halo-campaign-evolved/9N683TDT5M7R/0010" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Microsoft Store</a> on July 28. It will also be available via Game Pass.</p><p>Watch the trailer below.</p><h2><span>Cinematic Story Trailer</span></h2><p><iframe title="Halo: Campaign Evolved | Cinematic Story Trailer" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0MxBFXH2a_U?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div>

        
    
